metadata.name: Envision
metadata.description:
"The power of your dreams can take you to unknown worlds of abundance. You have the power to envision a life of magnificence and greatness"  

From a moment of magic in the beautiful mountains of New Zealand, this moment in itself invigorated a spark in me that I can make my dreams a reality. The moon reminds me of the beauty of life, sometimes we must go through phases of hardships to be whole again just like the moon.

Open edition  

artist: Joanne Hollings
